Transmutation
Level: Brd 1, Drd 1, Rgr 1, Sor/Wiz 1
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 1 minute/level
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: No
With the aid of Rabbit Feet, you can pass silently around attentive guards or sneak through creaky-floored rooms. The spell softens footfalls, quiets loose equipment, and otherwise
allows you to move silently.
The spell adds +2/level of the caster (maximum +18) to any Move Silently checks.